    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an unrivaled example of automotive excellence, this vehicle arrives in pristine, showroom condition. Meticulously preserved and maintained to the highest standards, it offers a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer who demands perfection. From the flawless exterior finish to the immaculate, odor-free interior, every detail reflects a history of uncompromising care. This is an investment-grade specimen that delivers a new-car experience at a significant pre-owned value. Experience the pinnacle of quality and performance in a vehicle that truly stands in a class of its own.",
      "price": 48950.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lovers! It truly breaks my heart to even think about parting with this absolute gem, but it's time for her to find a new home. I\u2019ve babied this beauty since day one\u2014she\u2019s lived a pampered life in a climate-controlled garage and has only ever seen hand-washes on clear Sunday mornings. It honestly feels like stepping back in time when you get behind the wheel; the finish is breathtaking and the drive is as smooth as silk. You might find a microscopic speck if you really go looking, but she\u2019s as close to showroom-perfect as you\u2019ll ever find. I\u2019d love for you to come by, have a chat, and see for yourself why I\u2019m so proud of this one!",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This is a concours-level build for the discerning pilot who demands zero-tolerance engineering. Benefiting from a comprehensive top-end refresh, the valvetrain is whisper-quiet with zero lash, and the compression across all cylinders is within a negligible variance. We\u2019ve optimized the power delivery with a custom-mapped ECU and a lightened flywheel that allows the engine to spin up with surgical precision and immediate throttle response. The chassis has been reinforced for maximum torsional rigidity, paired with 3-way adjustable coilovers that have been corner-balanced for perfectly neutral handling. Every suspension bushing has been replaced with high-durometer polyurethane to ensure razor-sharp turn-in. The paint depth is exceptional, and the cabin retains its factory-fresh tactile feedback. This is a mechanical masterpiece that has been over-maintained to ensure it consistently outperforms its original factory specifications.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Showroom floor quality. Zero flaws. Pure performance. Priced to move today. First come, first served.",
      "price": 43000.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into a time capsule of automotive elegance. This isn't just a car; it\u2019s a preserved masterpiece that hums with the quiet confidence of a legacy reborn. Every curve of its shimmering silhouette catches the light like liquid silk, leading your eyes to an interior that smells of rich, untouched heritage and whispered luxury. To drive this vehicle is to command the road with a grace that modern machines have long since forgotten. It feels as though it rolled off the showroom floor only yesterday, waiting for a pilot who understands that true soul cannot be manufactured\u2014it must be curated. Own a piece of history that looks, feels, and breathes as if the years never passed.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
